Name
       timing_extract_model_include_applied_load_in_characterization_range

Syntax
       timing_extract_model_include_applied_load_in_characterization_range

       {true | false}

       Default: true

       Specifies  that  the  actual load visible to the timer that will be in-
       cluded in the load characterization range for path end points.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

